column2: Lazy load XT is a jQuery plugin for images, videos and other media

column5:
Merge pull request #107 from vasani-arpit/master

Removed extra bracket
improved support of native srcset attribute; removed support of "h" suffix
fix tests ('lazied' attribute is removed after image is displayed)
fix parsing of commas in srcset (issue #60)
disable loading of images in `pageshow` event if autoInit is disabled
add `lazyloadall` event to load all images
update grunt packages, use jit-grunt to build

Merge pull request #61 from msaggiorato/patch-1

Remove dataLazied from the removed elements

Merge pull request #69 from filleokus/patch-1

Fix out-of-date link anchors in README.md

Fix out-of-date link anchors in README.md

Just changed the link anchors to point to the correct parts of the README.md

Remove dataLazied from the removed elements

This is so that they're not detected as duplicates if they're reattached to the DOM in the future.

Merge pull request #30 from aitherios/aitherios-patch-readme

Updating Responsive images anchor in Readme.md
Updating Responsive images anchor in Readme.md
dev version of DOMtastic with jQuery-compatible interface for filter() and each()
rename forceLoad->forceShow to don't interfere with forceLoad in outer scope
update min DOMtastic version in README

fix tests
(@todo: fix tests with Zepto and DOMtastic)
remove Google+ Profile widget from widget-iframe demo (disabled by Google)
fix set of img src in picture addon
trigger update on browser's tab activation
bind to both window and document (as scroll event doesn't bubble), fix issue #3
fix error in the case of undefined width attribute
Fix support of lazyload/lazyerror events in picture addon
Fix support of lazyload/lazyerror events in srcset addon (issue #2)
partial fix infinite demo in Opera Mini
"no longer supported" notice in simple version
add onstart handler and lazystart event
comment oncomplete property to reduce minified size (currently null and undefined have identical effect)
save forceLoad status to options.forceLoad (for external check, e.g. in infinite.htm demo)
update demo for fadein, spinner, and horizontal animations
fix srcset addon (because of change of default value for tselector option)
rename autoLoad to forceLoad (to don't confuse with autoInit)
add fadein and spinner effects to src
fix autoload addon to use lazycomplete event
use natural ordering in elements array (speed up adding new elements)
trigger lazy* event after global on* handler

rename lazyloadall to lazycomplete
add support of global oncomplete handler

remove classNojs in flavour of options.oninit.removeClass
support lazy-hidden and lazy-loaded css classes for effects
change selector to img[data-src] (to don't affect usual images like tracking images, etc.)

reduce minified size by using global lazyLoadXT='lazyLoadXT' variable
fallback docElement to document.body in old browsers
call getBoundingClientRect() in non-force mode only
move 'load error' to global constant to reduce minified size
use src property to reduce size
invert condition (exactly as described in jsDoc)
speed up work by direct using get/setAttribute and getBoundingClientRect() instead of jQuery methods
fix work in BB5 and iOS3 (no support in jQuery 1.8+)
handle touchmove event for better response on mobile devices
load all images in some mobile browsers without scroll event
force loading of images in Opera Mini
new `checkDuplicates` option, speed up work with jQuery
proxy overrides parameter in the case of $(window).lazyLoadXT({...})
fix: $el.lazyLoadXT should be single object (required by picture addon)
add examples of horizontal scroll and infinite scroll to README
fix check of right and bottom viewport margins
update description for responsive images addons
split srcset addon into srcset and picture
move tag check to children() filter
srcset widget: add support of <picture> element
fix get of element's srcAttr option
pass original jQuery object to event handler
save options to jQuery elements's lazyLoadXT property
remove load/error handler after first triggering
documentElement is DOM1, remove fallback to body
fix removing blank characters in grunt-combine
support of "self-lazy" widget (empty value for data-lazy-widget)
Add Google Maps Lite to demo
code modifications to reduce minified size
add support of per element options (blankImage, classNojs, srcAttr, edgeX, edgeY, visibleOnly)

move addElement to $.fn.lazyLoadXT
remove support of selector parameter in $.fn.lazyLoadXT
remove "src" from bower install (as all addons were moved to dist)
remove blankImage option from simple version
script addon: L/Lb/Le functions, use span instead of div, fix moving nodes
background addon: support $.lazyLoadXT.bgAttr attribute, fix $this definition to e.target
Add `<input type="image">` to list of supported tags
use Lb() to mark open tag and Le for close one, (L)azy(b)egin/(L)azy(e)nd
Simplified version of Lazy Load XT, without support of lazy events
mark lazy images with script element instead of data-src attribute
deferred run of timeoutLazyElements (to prevent possible loops)
fix in-DOM check for browsers where document is not Node
add support of prefix (base pathname) in data-srcset-base attribute

$.lazyLoadXT.videoPoster for data-poster attribute;
$.lazyLoadXT.srcAttr for data-src attribute
example of autoload of all images after a delay
fix queue of next check by checkLazyElements->triggerEvent
add "forceEvent" option to force loading of elements
use unminified code in demo (for debug purposes)
update video-related demos to use new code
update tests to load "extra" video code
reorder "if" to check fastest condition first
add events support (Note: handler names in options are lowercase now)
add installation with Bower and NPM
